{"tid":2411784,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[化妝技巧請教] 參考人物:谷婭溦","createTime":"2021-02-17T14:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T07:06:46.000Z","uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51447039d634cf6fa424e4aeed5851154b17b9c8","tid":2411784,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"首先我想講我就唔係谷婭溦（原名：谷微）嘅fans嚟嘅，喺幾個鐘之前我都知佢係咩水<br />\n話說我啱啱開spotify聽住歌做嘢，隨機咁聽到佢首新歌《習慣》，咁覺得佢都唱得幾好聽，跟住我就google睇下佢係邊個嚟，先知道佢原來係大陸人嚟，嚟咗香港發展，呢啲只係背景故事嚟，表過不提<br />\n重點係當我見到佢google啲相，我好驚訝點解啲相嘅差異可以咁大<br />\n呢啲係佢專輯嘅樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQL1AvX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQL1AvX.jpg&h=14f5d819&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqNza5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqNza5r.jpg&h=9ac3ae0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R71cHb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR71cHb6.jpg&h=13316e41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪幾靚幾索呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n唔好J住&hellip;&hellip;google仲有佢未出道/冇化妝嘅相：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSVkQ6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSVkQ6Z.jpg&h=67469f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAT24tK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAT24tK.jpg&h=485ca309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nＷhat the....<br />\n所以話女人化妝嘅威力有幾大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請教下絲打們，到底佢/佢個化妝師係做咗啲咩先化到咁靚？<br />\n<br />\n參考照片：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QKh3OXG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQKh3OXG.jpg&h=af4bf367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ecOZ4m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ecOZ4m.jpg&h=990fb373&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6509fc01ec46226748508d6d4e0c57423eeb90c","tid":2411784,"uid":149041,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"Groupmate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2003651a38b186031c12ce35031f0aff9a339701","tid":2411784,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f6509fc01ec46226748508d6d4e0c57423eeb90c","tid":2411784,"uid":149041,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"Groupmate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"呃&hellip;咁佢平時係咪都會化到咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489bbd8350c3ee9ddd59f8f7a359b2afe3280f18","tid":2411784,"uid":199592,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"整容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8924cd5e61d7abf42bdce5ea42070868fe9fd9c","tid":2411784,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"佢唱歌好一般<br />\n<br />\n武漢音樂學院同花花同校<br />\n<br />\n花花勁佢好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab0d660e8ac40973562751fcef318815602b9f8","tid":2411784,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"美國波士頓音樂學院<br />\n<br />\n都唱成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />理論派來？"},{"pid":"5463c8ed676848199546171d755a8ef987317356","tid":2411784,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"489bbd8350c3ee9ddd59f8f7a359b2afe3280f18","tid":2411784,"uid":199592,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"整容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n我上面只係post咗佢化得好睇嘅相出嚟<br />\n佢有啲化得唔好睇，個樣就差好遠<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190105/photo/bkn-20190105191731929-0105_00862_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190105191731929-0105_00862_001_01p.jpg&h=b39a46e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我先以為佢係靠化妝先整到咁靚<br />\n想拆解佢化妝化得靚嘅技巧，偷下師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06d02e12f22a0b2322de12c6e9b4b324c78dc38","tid":2411784,"uid":256566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"主要都係p圖先會做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整容化妝都只係好小部分"},{"pid":"7ab8efa51c51f89a7b66b9042f2f7aa08d6e3663","tid":2411784,"uid":5891,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a8924cd5e61d7abf42bdce5ea42070868fe9fd9c","tid":2411784,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:20:17.000Z","msg":"佢唱歌好一般<br />\n<br />\n武漢音樂學院同花花同校<br />\n<br />\n花花勁佢好多倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"花花即係邊個嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得谷婭溦有幾首歌都幾好聽《聽海》、《習慣》、翻唱《味道》<br />\n佢仲有首係用廣東話唱嘅《哭牆》，鄉音未脫，怪得嚟我又接受到，其實係呢首歌我先意識到佢應該唔係香港人嚟，好明顯佢唱普通話歌係好聽過粵語歌<br />\n但廣東話咬字未係好好呢點我本身並唔反感，就好似王菲唱粵語歌都係有缺失，但反而係咁為佢嘅唱腔增添咗獨特嘅魅力<br />\n我重申我唔係佢fans嚟，只係我啱啱search過呢幾首歌覺得幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然個post重點唔係討論呢樣嘢，但其實我都幾鍾意聽歌，花花啲歌如果都好聽，希望你都可以推介畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw,我啱啱又係隨機聽到位叫江佩蓉嘅台灣歌手，又係有幾首都好正：《放手》、《只要你放樂》、《比我對你更好的人》、《非法入境》，仲未聽哂佢啲歌，可能仲有更好嘅"},{"pid":"e9a655f63deffa182b673e1c518fef68f5085345","tid":2411784,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"